<span class="style26">
walkside, lost (2015)<br></span>
<span class="style28">for Slagwerk Den Haag<br>
three percussionists, electronics, and video processing<br>
Text by Darcie Dennigan
<center><span class="style27">Commissioned by Gaudeamus Muziekweek<br><br>
World Premiere: Utrecht, Netherlands - 9/13/2015<br>
</span></center>
    <br>



